Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.00,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,喂喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:22.32,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,可恶 看不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.50,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,小姐 请您小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.07,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗已经开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,无线电也瘫痪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,黑骸的出战指令也不知道下达了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 由希奈 不用换上战斗服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:02.78,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.42,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,你在害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:30.77,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,亏你这样的胆小鬼还能当驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:36.12,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,就算是我…剑之介…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:40.15,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,不过那也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.25,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,恐慌吧 畏惧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:50.00,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,你的眼中冲刺着恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.45,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,不错啊 不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:58.12,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,那可是人所有表情之中我最中意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:05.50,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,生命逝去的那刹那 将死之人的求饶的眼神让我欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:15.65,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,放心吧 我不杀你 还有事情得让你做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.12,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,快走 往下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.92,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,不是去黑骸那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:35.20,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,弗朗格尔待会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:58.80,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,总算让我找到了 枢石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:04.07,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,枢？ 那个就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 那边的 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:27.42,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,这破烂东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:38.77,Default,Rita,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.77,Default,Rita,0,0,0,,一层倾斜式电梯的乘坐口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.02,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,去地下了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:47.36,Default,Beth,0,0,0,,挖掘场那发来目击到疑为由希奈和一名不明男子的身影的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.57,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,立刻让Alpha小队和Bravo小队赶过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.57,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,由希奈她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.77,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,下令尽全力抓捕福斯纳尼以及确保白羽由希奈的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:03.02,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,若出现可能危及生命的情况 允许狙击福斯纳尼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:10.40,Default,Carrie,0,0,0,,请等一等 为了今后的调查研究 我要求活捉福斯纳尼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.12,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,保证由希奈和剑之介的安全是最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:18.82,Default,Carrie,0,0,0,,剑之介？ 你相信他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:19.77,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:22.47,Default,Carrie,0,0,0,,有什么根据？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:24.92,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,没有具体的根据
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:28.50,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,但他是一名武士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.15,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,狗屁武士死哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.52,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,我来阻止这长臂猿的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:52.00,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,你趁机拿枪爆了他那让人火大的菊花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.97,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,还是那么的没品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.40,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:12.47,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,由于这是老式机型 必须要两个人才会活动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.22,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,所以就我和你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:22.30,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,不过在那之前 先得让你解除那家伙和弗朗格尔的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.67,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,再与定下我的契约取而代之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:29.84,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,启动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.10,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,剑之介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:48.45,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,放那女人走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.80,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:53.75,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.62,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,你们是叫它黑骸来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:58.87,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,物归原主了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:03.55,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,还有这驾驶员女孩我也要带走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:05.20,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.40,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,要是你敢伤她一根汗毛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:12.95,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我拼了命也要把你送下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.39,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:33.82,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,你莫非是鹫羽家三足首领 斋藤弥久善道？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:35.32,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:41.32,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,你不是效忠鹫羽家的吗 我可在城下见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:46.97,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么 而且不是你背叛我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:50.17,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我从未曾与你们为伍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:57.32,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,那为什么你能驱使黑骸 这东西唯有吾等同胞才能驾驭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.42,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:12.67,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,倒是你为何沦落成鬼的爪牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.05,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,鬼？ 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:21.15,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,果然你的记忆被篡改了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:25.67,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,什么 那不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.40,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,那不可能是假的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:35.50,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,剑之介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.70,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,死心吧 你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:06.05,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,那至少把她拉做垫背
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:44.95,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,到此为止了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:52.52,Default,Fusnarnie,0,0,0,,决不能耻辱地苟活于世…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:12.10,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:41.55,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:43.32,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 重新开始作业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:01.30,Default,Aramata,0,0,0,,这就是他们所说的枢么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.50,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,根据由希奈所说 福斯纳尼见到这东西之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:07.77,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,说了一句「终于找到了」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.35,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,这个到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:16.30,Default,Aramata,0,0,0,,试试以这些碎片复原整体原貌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:22.22,Default,Carrie,0,0,0,,他的尸体由我们回收
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:28.95,Default,Heath,0,0,0,,了解 福斯纳尼和剑之介 到底谁说的是事实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:33.62,Default,Carrie,0,0,0,,事到如今真相已石沉大海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:38.07,Default,Heath,0,0,0,,内讧或是封口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:39.60,Default,Carrie,0,0,0,,现在也无从得知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:46.97,Default,Carrie,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 需要对那个叫剑之介的青年进行严密地监视了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.67,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,人外有人 天外有天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:06.37,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,索菲 给赤城留个言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:08.82,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,要留给赤城同学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.22,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,该说些什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:15.75,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,我想想…随时接受你的挑战？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:18.80,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,还望勿来打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:23.07,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,不愧是GAUS的现役驾驶员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:30.60,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,你们走着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:51.57,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.02,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,完败啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.22,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,你倒是先冷静一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:16:00.23,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,就算你在这游戏里赢过索菲 也不意味着你能成为驾驶员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:03.97,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.05,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:08.12,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.87,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,那家伙 真想当驾驶员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.55,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,怎么可能 应该是个冷笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:17.60,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:20.27,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.22,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,爸 你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,刚下班回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.13,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,姑且说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:33.77,Default,Aramata,0,0,0,,我已经决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.52,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,成为驾驶员乘上GAUS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:42.65,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:47.65,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,我有那个资质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:54.52,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,因为我轻而易举就在游戏中心拿下了驾驶员游戏的最高分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是真这么想的话 那先成就些什么再说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:02.40,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,那你就一旁守望着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:21.90,Default,Koharu,0,0,0,,他居然没要求咖喱添饭 每天稳定地就只吃一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.62,Default,Koharu,0,0,0,,不对 稳定这么少肯定不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:31.32,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,一天到晚闷在家中 屁股上都要生苔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.95,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,呀 座地藏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.67,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,座地藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:42.72,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,很久很久以前 某座村庄中有个男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:46.30,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,他日复一日地整天坐在走廊上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:50.15,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,每当有人问道「你在干什么呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.82,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,他就回「修行」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:59.52,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,可突然有一天 他发现自己的身体变成了石头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:02.37,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,「不好了」男孩慌慌张张大声呼喊道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:07.37,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,「神明啊 佛祖啊 俺错了 这么下去的话都不能去祭典了」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.45,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,说着说着大哭了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.80,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,这个时候 神明动了怜悯之心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:16.87,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,赐予他每年两次变回原来的样子的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:21.35,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,渐渐地这男孩就被人称为座地藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.74,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,那是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:24.10,Default,uncle,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:29.87,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,趁你还没有变回石头的时候 到外面去活动活动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:32.47,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,明天能不能陪我出一趟门呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.62,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,哦哟 这是要约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.65,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.22,Default,Koharu,0,0,0,,别害羞别害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:40.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,不对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:47.95,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,确实应该是这附近才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.95,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,喂 刚才就走过这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.60,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,诶 你带着那是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:57.22,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,明显是为了找地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:02.17,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.17,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:06.55,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:07.55,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:09.83,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,由希奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:13.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.57,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.82,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,咦 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:21.67,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,可能找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:22.60,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.15,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,大概是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:42.00,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,应该是在这的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:44.65,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,确实好像有过什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:47.82,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,消失不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.92,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,你在这看到了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:54.87,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,就是有点像秘密基地的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:58.90,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,里面有着许多昭和年代电器样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:01.37,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,昭和年代电器？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:05.12,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,电视还是显像管的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:06.60,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,显像管？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:12.30,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,还有感觉看到了爸爸的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:18.05,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,那个难道是错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:24.00,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我之前也跟你说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:28.85,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,由于爸爸的原因 我被叫做牛皮大王的女儿在学校被人欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:29.70,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:35.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,所以我一直叫爸爸骗子 并且狠狠地说了他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:39.77,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,之后也没怎么跟他说过话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:46.12,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,虽然已经这么久了 但是我在想要是当时能跟父亲多说说话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:47.40,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,谢谢你 剑之介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:51.47,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:54.57,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,因为你遵守了我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:55.90,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,约定？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:57.92,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,诶 你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.57,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,你不是说过要保护我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:07.55,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,那个时候 我以为我肯定要被杀了 非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:12.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,但我又在想 要是你来了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:15.50,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,结果真的就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:20.17,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我从心底觉得「啊 得救了」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.90,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我来保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:27.35,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我可不会说第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:31.47,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:35.60,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,诶 咖喱？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:41.15,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,这个嘛 小春说我喜欢就特别为我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.00,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,啊 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:46.12,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,饭团就该配 干货 鲑鱼 梅干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:48.12,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,配上咖喱完全是邪道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.57,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,你还真是陈腐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:52.15,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,轮不到你说我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:56.57,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,这什么东西 饺子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:59.37,Default,Koharu,0,0,0,,小春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:23.28,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}誰も皆 孤独なStray Cat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:25.98,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}授かった その名前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:34.04,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}片切符(かたきっぷ)に 時を 渡るの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:38.40,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}鏡越しの弱さ背け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:41.34,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}逃避行は 赦(ゆる)されない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:49.90,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)} 想う故に 心臓が叫ぶわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:22:58.88,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}Don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:02.14,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}傷みを伴(ともな)ったって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:06.20,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}このひと足から 変えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:10.36,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}感情論じゃ 語れない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:13.96,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}私のリアル曲げないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:17.24,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}「まだ生きたい」と願うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:21.54,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}あなたと出逢えた あの日から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:25.31,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}心の深層(なか) 呼吸してる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.31,0:23:29.24,Kuromukuro ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fad(250,250)}温もりが在るから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:34.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,算是收纳黑骸的挂架？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:23:39.12,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,原本的目的是用于调查 2想要用来发射的话相当麻烦
